snippet.title: Mayor Bones' Pumpkin Festival is BACK for 2022!
snippet.description:
Mayor Bone's Pumpkin Festival is BACK for 2022! 🎃

🌃 Explore and decorate a new area!
👻 Customize your ghost for online play!
🏆 Award badges to pumpkins!
🤔 Guess other players' pumpkins from their hints!

It's pay-what-you-want (free even!)
👉 https://adamgryu.itch.io/pumpkin-carver
